Requires:
	- nbspgislib or nbsp
	- rclone

Typical sequence

satrclone -v -w /var/satftp /etc/satftp/zone.list
satrcloneimg -v -w /var/satftp 

or the equivalent

satrclone -v -n -w /var/satftp 
satrcloneasc -v -w /var/satftp /etc/satftp/zone.list
satrcloneimg -v -w /var/satftp

If we want to restrict the channels, for example only channels 1 and 3-5,
we add the cmd line option

-c 1-1,3-5

to satrclone.
